>
  <!-- Left Image -->
  <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
    <Image
      src={MissionImg}
      alt="Expert Pipe Welding and Installation"
      class="w-full h-[300px] md:h-[400px] object-cover rounded-xl shadow-md"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Right Text -->
  <div
    class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left"
  >
    <h2
      class="text-[#0B2545] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-[4px] mb-4"
    >
      Why Choose PB&J
    </h2>

    <p class="text-gray-600 text-base md:text-lg leading-7 mb-6">
      PB&J Contracting Ltd is a leading water management specialist based in New
      Zealand, delivering expert design, build, and maintenance services for
      irrigation systems nationwide.
      <br /><br />
      We specialise in creating efficient, reliable solutions for premier golf courses
      and productive horticultural operations. From conceptual design of pump stations
